  "detailed_description": "Player QQ Group: 562345294<br><br>Are you looking for a simple jumping game?<br>Are you confused by the gimmicky game interface?<br>Now you can play Jumping!<br><strong> Gameplay</strong><br>You just need to press the button to control the genie to jump over the gap! Don't let it fall!<br>Complete the game's levels with a few jumps!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082440/extras/20855ce25944167c1572765269c53e8a.poster.avif?t=1743741242\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082440/extras/20855ce25944167c1572765269c53e8a.webm?t=1743741242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082440/extras/20855ce25944167c1572765269c53e8a.mp4?t=1743741242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> Game Mechanics</strong><br>And don't touch platforms of specific colors at the same time! That's one of the ways you can fail!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082440/extras/9a8df3684b2cec990d3e5338a990dfa1.poster.avif?t=1743741242\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082440/extras/9a8df3684b2cec990d3e5338a990dfa1.webm?t=1743741242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082440/extras/9a8df3684b2cec990d3e5338a990dfa1.mp4?t=1743741242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* Dodge gaps! Don't let your controlled sprites fall!<br>* Make sure there's a foothold! Don't fall on blocks of different colors!<br>* Requires the player's agile reflexes! Hurry up and challenge!<br>* Easy to control! Just remember two keystrokes!<br>* Pixel style meets your love of minimalist style!<br>What are you thinking about, does it take your hesitation to play such a game that can be played by cats in the house? Of course not!",
